---
name: Complex Password Requirements
description: Uses positive lookaheads to ensure passwords have 1 lowercase letter, 1 uppercase letter, 1 number, 1 special character and be at least 8 characters long. Note: Do not rely on regex for validating passwords!
source: https://digitalfortress.tech/tips/top-15-commonly-used-regex/
flavor: regexp
---

(?=(.*[0-9]))(?=.*[\!@#$%^&*()\\[\]{}\-_+=~`|:;"'<>,./?])(?=.*[a-z])(?=(.*[A-Z]))(?=(.*)).{8,}
